{"tid":1384840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好約前線手足食飯","createTime":"2019-07-30T03:04:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T04:15:45.000Z","uid":282346,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"792db6def1df3664fb6c2790de172192dae7e9a8","tid":1384840,"uid":282346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:04:59.000Z","msg":"明白大家都好想幫手<br />\n但請大家唔好約出黎食野<br />\n避免黑警利用呢個機會接觸前線手足同套料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同時亦唔知會唔會有黑警扮前線手足<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">前線手足請唔好同陌生人講任何自己夢遊既經歷</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n想幫前線手足仲有好多匿名既方法<br />\n例如課金買多啲裝備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁佢地咪可以留返啲錢食飯<br />\n再唔係見到佢地既直接幫佢地靜靜雞埋單或者加餸<br />\n去前線派coupon/gift card派完就走<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>光復香港 <br />\n時代革命</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"20801888a79ce7859a1eaecc7bcde82d5748b300","tid":1384840,"uid":115977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>8月5日大罷工</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6d201889aa0ab06bccfe29b3d414e597860ea1e8","tid":1384840,"uid":282346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:07:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"b980f112b9759e2e3304cfec8802372b3db82981","tid":1384840,"uid":282346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:12:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52137499e1f813ac8ca177a2b4698b861c25a6d4","tid":1384840,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:14:21.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"3ba67602528bfb02e5c5a66c2b23e7ba885c3689","tid":1384840,"uid":282346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T03:19:58.00